What did you think of American Gods Season 3? 

I think they should have never gotten rid of Mr. Nancy.

What really made me realize for the first time that Mr.World was actually Loki, is when he tells Technical Boy, “Trickery is what I do best”. It had never occurred to me up until that very moment, that Loki could have been Mr.World all along. It seems crazy naive in retrospect that hadn't crossed my mind considering how much Mr.World transforms into other people just like Loki.
Seeing how much of a shit storm of a production and how long it took season 3 to be put out I can’t wait for season 4 in 2047
I hate dead wife, really not happy if she ends up being Shadows "soulmate". She might as well been working for Wednesday,  she set everything in motion.
